Description: Papyrus fragment bearing 1 line of a Coptic text written along the fibres (recto) and 8 lines against the fibres (verso). EA 75363, 75364, 75365, 75366, 75367, 75368, 75369, 75370, 75371, 75372, 75373, 75374, 75375 are mounted together.
